  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, NameTag, NetworkRef<BaseDStabNetwork<?,?>>, DynamicSimuAlgorithm, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject

    public class DynamicSimuAlgorithmImpl
extends NetworkRefImpl<BaseDStabNetwork<?,?>>
implements DynamicSimuAlgorithm
    An implementation of the model object 'Dynamic Simu Algorithm'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Total Simu Time Sec
    • Simu Step Sec
    • Simu Method
    • Output Per Steps
    • Output Filtered
    • Output Var Id List
    • Disable Dynamic Event
    • Ref Machine
    • Aclf Algorithm
    • Simu Output Handler
    • Script Output Handler
    • Dynamic Event Handler
